# British Airways Reviews Dashboard

This project provides a comprehensive visualization of customer reviews for British Airways, based on multiple metrics such as overall rating, cabin staff service, entertainment, food, ground service, seat comfort, and value for money. The dashboard is built using Tableau and includes interactive components for in-depth data exploration.

![British Airways Reviews Dashboard](/Users/musticodes/Desktop/tableau_portfolio_project/Dashboard%201.png)

## Key Features

- **Average Ratings**: Displays the average ratings for various aspects such as cabin staff service, entertainment, food, ground service, and seat comfort.
- **Trends Over Time**: Visualizes the average overall rating by month from March 2016 to October 2023.
- **Geographical Distribution**: A map showing the average overall rating by country.
- **Aircraft Comparison**: Bar chart comparing the average overall ratings across different aircraft types and the number of reviews per aircraft.

## Filters

- **Metric Selection**: Choose from metrics such as overall rating, cabin staff service, entertainment, etc.
- **Date Range**: The data covers the period from March 2016 to October 2023.
- **Seat Type, Traveler Type, Aircraft, and Continent**: Use these filters to refine the data based on specific categories.

## Tableau Public Link

You can explore the interactive dashboard [here](https://public.tableau.com/views/BritishAirwaysReviews_17365663703890/Dashboard1?:language=de-DE&:sid=&:redirect=auth&:display_count=n&:origin=viz_share_link).

## How to Use

1. Open the Tableau Public link to interact with the dashboard.
2. Use the filters on the left to customize the data visualization according to your preferences.
3. Hover over the visualizations for detailed insights and data points.

## Project Purpose

This dashboard aims to provide an accessible and user-friendly way to analyze customer feedback for British Airways. It allows stakeholders to identify trends, evaluate customer satisfaction, and make data-driven decisions to improve service quality.

